          <li><a href="/repair">维修日</a></li>
          <li><a href="/calendar">技术讲座</a></li>
          <li><a href="/calendar">NWDC</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="hp-footer-col">
        <h4 class="hp-footer-heading">社区</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/about">关于我们</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about#join">加入我们</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about#members">成员</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="hp-footer-col">
        <h4 class="hp-footer-heading">资源</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/blog">博客</a></li>
          <li><a href="/calendar">活动日历</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/nbtca" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://docs.nbtca.space" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">文档</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="hp-footer-col">
        <h4 class="hp-footer-heading">关于</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/about#vision">愿景</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about#mission">使命</a></li>
          <li><a href="mailto:contact@nbtca.space">联系我们</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="hp-footer-col">
        <h4 class="hp-footer-heading">关注</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/about#wechat">微信公众号</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://qm.qq.com/q/djgZhpnlzW" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">QQ 群</a></li>
          <li><a href="/rss.xml" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">RSS</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hp-footer-bottom">
      <p>Copyright &copy; 2002&ndash;{year} NBTCA &middot; 宁波理工学院计算机协会 &middot; 技术与人文的交汇</p>
      <a href="https://beian.miit.gov.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">浙ICP备2021030831号</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .hp-footer {
    background: #f5f5f7;
    border-top: 1px solid #d2d2d7;
  }

  .hp-footer-inner {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 24px 32px;
  }

  .hp-footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 32px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hp-footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .hp-footer-heading {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .hp-footer-col ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .hp-footer-col a {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #6e6e73;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .hp-footer-col a:hover {
    color: #1d1d1f;
  }

  .hp-footer-bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid #d2d2d7;
    padding-top: 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .hp-footer-bottom {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
  }

  .hp-footer-bottom p,
  .hp-footer-bottom a {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #6e6e73;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .hp-footer-bottom a:hover {
    color: #1d1d1f;
  }
</style>
